15,01Lessons Learned

15,01He walked down the darkened hallway toward the beacon that shone from
15,01the last room on the right.  His mind was filled with both fear and 
15,01great anticipation.  It had been a month since he last dared enter
15,01that chamber, and had sworn he never would again.   So completely
15,01helpless he had felt!  The thing that drew him so strongly was the
15,01very same thing he imagined would be his undoing, HER.

15,01She was not anything magnificent by virtue of face or form, and yet,
15,01she was an incredible mixture of characteristics that never failed to
15,01leave him in dire need of attention.  Her affect on him was always
15,01immediate and overwhelming, he was a lost man in her presence, so
15,01great was her power over him.  

15,01Tonight he vowed it would be different, but deep within himself, he 
15,01knew it was hopeless.  She would have her way, and he would allow it,
15,01in fact plead for it.  He only hoped that she was not in one of those
15,01moods where there was simply no pleasing her.  The last time she had
15,01been in that mood, it had nearly killed him.  He recalled, with
15,01amazing clarity, just what it was like.  He also remembered that he
15,01had never felt such incredible sensations in all his 25 years on
15,01earth.

15,01As he came to the bathroom on the left, he went in and started to 
15,01dress for the meeting with his Mistress.  He was not allowed to show
15,01up unless he was properly attired, and he did not want to pay the 
15,01penalty she had established for failing to comply.  He was fond of
15,01his genitals, thank you, and would comply with her wishes.  He was 
15,01thankful she was not one of those who would demand he dress in satin
15,01and silk lingerie, he didn't see himself as the type.  The clothing
15,01that she mandated he wear was actually very comfortable - a black
15,01t-back and a black bow tie, nothing else.

15,01Now, as he neared the chamber where his Mistress lingered, he began to
15,01shake.  He was certain she would punish him for his transgressions
15,01and he was fairly certain she would use him to her total satisfaction
15,01as well.

15,01She had only sent him away without fulfillment twice.  The first time
15,01was when he was still in the stage of proving his worth to her.  He
15,01had failed to act upon her order quickly enough, so she had simply 
15,01teased and provoked him until he was within seconds of release and
15,01then she had simply sent him home, no kind words, no kiss, nothing for
15,01him at all except the lesson that when she asked for something it was
15,01to be taken as a direct order.  The other time was when he had failed
15,01to contain himself the previous visit, and she made him endure hours
15,01of sensual torture.  He had handled that situation as soon as he got
15,01home, and you can bet that it was HER that he thought of as he did so.

15,01He lowered his eyes, put his hands behind his back, and stepped lightly
15,01into the room.

15,01"Mistress, I am here, may I please serve you?" he said in a rather low
15,01tone.

15,01The sound of wicked laughter filled the dungeon then, and she walked
15,01over to him and slapped his backside hard with her open hand.

15,01"You are here just in time, slave.  I have a surprise for you." and 
15,01the wicked laughter resumed.  He dared not look up without her
15,01permission, and when he heard the distinct sound of small machinery, 
15,01his curiosity was piqued and he almost tried to sneak a peak.
15,01Almost, but not quite.  He knew better, he remembered the way her
15,01paddle felt on his bare backside.

15,01He heard the muffled sounds of pleasure coming from further within
15,01the dungeon, and longed to see what was hapening, and to whom.  He
15,01stood, head down, shaking - again in both anticipation and fear.  He
15,01waited for her instruction.  Her instruction to look up never came at
15,01all.  He stood there for a long time with all kinds of images running
15,01through his mind, until finally she approached him and repeatedly
15,01slapped his other cheek hard enough that it stung like ant bites.
15,01When she stopped, she said:

15,01"I had something very pleasurable in mind for you, but you upset me
15,01when you did not show up as planned, so you will need to prove you are
15,01worthy all over again before I bless you with my favor.  You will
15,01remember not to stay away so long in the future, won't you, slave?"

